A small thing: If you are targeting Chrome, or modern browsers in general, use<p><pre><code>  Object.defineProperty(Object.prototype, 'grep', {
    enumerable: false,
    value: /* ... */
  });
</code></pre>
rather than<p><pre><code>  Object.prototype.grep = /* ... */
</code></pre>
This way, your 'grep' does not pollute for () loops.
